# function logCheckoutEvent

## arg cartId: string
The identifier of the cart that triggered the event.

## arg event: {CheckoutEvent}
The event type and timestamp to record.

## error AppError(IO_ERROR)
Thrown if the audit log write fails.

## flow

1. Serialize the event with cartId and a UTC timestamp.
2. Write the serialized record to the audit log store.
3. If the write fails, wrap the underlying error and throw AppError(IO_ERROR).
